(34608, '_transient_connect_updates', 'a:44:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:17:"pl-section-lander";s:9:"post_name";s:17:"pl-section-lander";s:10:"post_title";s:6:"Lander";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.5";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 06:37:59";s:12:"post_content";s:333:"The Lander section is a great way to make a landing page that makes an impression. \nIt''s designed with very large, responsive heading type that quickly communicates your product. \nThe main CTA button supports downloads and ''post click'' video link.\nAlso, you can add lightboxed images underneath as a nice way to provide additional...";s:12:"product_link";s:55:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-lander/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"33a1c61daf7f7fbd3ab67cb26afb7f5f";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:54:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-lander.zip";}}}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:21:"pl-section-pricelines";s:9:"post_name";s:21:"pl-section-pricelines";s:10:"post_title";s:10:"PriceLines";s:7:"version";s:6:"5.0.11";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 06:42:26";s:12:"post_content";s:344:"Pricelines is an advanced pricing page section, with added options to help you convert customers. \nIt adds a responsive price plan listing that supports various details. \nSecond, you can add a nice feature listing to add additional support to what you''re selling (guaranteed, etc.. )\nFinally, it supports an FAQ so you can quickly answer any...";s:12:"product_link";s:59:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-pricelines/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"762eb1755ece5110fe2154de8ff5468b";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:58:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-pricelines.zip";}}}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:16:"pl-section-index";s:9:"post_name";s:16:"pl-section-index";s:10:"post_title";s:5:"Index";s:7:"version";s:6:"5.0.10";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 06:45:47";s:12:"post_content";s:327:"The Index section is a great way to add a grid of WordPress menus to a page. \nIt is also responsive and supports real time editing. \nThis section is ideal for use in the footer of your site, as you can show links to most your pages. \nFinally, you can add links to your social profiles very quickly and easily using the icons...";s:12:"product_link";s:54:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-index/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"ced7c590194bbeaba1dc3d16cfd34308";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:53:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-index.zip";}}}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:23:"pl-plugin-import-export";s:9:"post_name";s:23:"pl-plugin-import-export";s:10:"post_title";s:13:"Import Export";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.3";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-02-29 20:46:44";s:12:"post_content";s:106:"<p>Import and export your Platform 5 data with one handy tool, supports the Platform Templates Plugin.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:61:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-plugin-import-export/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"f3e8b073927434452b5e0686395bafe9";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:60:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-plugin-import-export.zip";}}}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:20:"pl-section-workswith";s:9:"post_name";s:20:"pl-section-workswith";s:10:"post_title";s:9:"WorksWith";s:7:"version";s:6:"5.0.10";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 06:49:59";s:12:"post_content";s:305:"<p>An advanced compatibility listing and details section for your product or service.</p>\n<p>Use custom post types to add new listings. Then you can use a variety of settings to control the level and meta information related to the listing. </p>\n<p>Supports compatibility level, videos, FAQs and more.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:58:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-workswith/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"9d1de6f024752ad51a030c267b2c2900";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:57:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-workswith.zip";}}}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:14:"pl-section-lax";s:9:"post_name";s:14:"pl-section-lax";s:10:"post_title";s:3:"Lax";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.4";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 06:54:00";s:12:"post_content";s:348:"Lax is a simple parallax section that will allow for parallaxed background images as the user scrolls down the page. \r\nIt supports nested sections as well as some basic content options. \r\nA very nice scroll effect that is sure to impress your users.\r\nNote: There are some issues when using this section with other sticky sections as it places an...";s:12:"product_link";s:52:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-lax/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"745b0eee3e16e20c89a40259248b887e";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:51:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-lax.zip";}}}i:6;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:19:"pl-section-teamwork";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"pl-section-teamwork";s:10:"post_title";s:8:"TeamWork";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.7";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-04 04:59:29";s:12:"post_content";s:348:"Overview\nA fully featured team page template section. Add team members with usernames.\n\nInstallation & Activation\nTeamWork can easily be downloaded from inside WordPress using Extend.\n\nDownload the plugin from Extend. It will now appear in your Plugins tab.\nClick Plugins, and find your TeamWork plugin (titled PageLines Section TeamWork).\nClick...";s:12:"product_link";s:57:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-teamwork/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"d705ccda9e40df61012fa25a58e252b8";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:56:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-teamwork.zip";}}}i:7;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:19:"pl-section-magazine";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"pl-section-magazine";s:10:"post_title";s:8:"Magazine";s:7:"version";s:6:"5.0.42";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 07:05:26";s:12:"post_content";s:250:"<p>Magazine is an AWESOME section for creating and managing your blog. </p>\n<p>Simply add to your blog page and your individual post pages and you''re on your way.</p>\n<p>Supports a variety of layouts and featured posts via WPs sticky post option.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:57:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-magazine/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"a282cfbfc1fda0b06acc3bc79d703f07";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:56:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-magazine.zip";}}}i:8;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:20:"pl-section-tourguide";s:9:"post_name";s:20:"pl-section-tourguide";s:10:"post_title";s:9:"TourGuide";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.6";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-02 08:31:50";s:12:"post_content";s:79:"<p>An advanced template section for creating a fully featured product tour.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:58:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-tourguide/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"a3a99f3ffb64cd2c6133afe0f97d7db1";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:57:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-tourguide.zip";}}}i:9;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:16:"pl-section-loops";s:9:"post_name";s:16:"pl-section-loops";s:10:"post_title";s:5:"Loops";s:7:"version";s:6:"5.0.18";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-04 04:58:24";s:12:"post_content";s:345:"Overview\nLoops is a powerful section for controlling the native WordPress loop and WP Query. With layout controls.\n\nInstallation & Activation\nLoops can easily be downloaded from inside WordPress using Extend.\n\nDownload the plugin from Extend. It will now appear in your Plugins tab.\nClick Plugins, and find your Loops plugin (titled PageLines...";s:12:"product_link";s:54:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-loops/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"4e29c3a172bec513958bd7b9a485abe3";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:53:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-loops.zip";}}}i:10;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:17:"pl-section-switch";s:9:"post_name";s:17:"pl-section-switch";s:10:"post_title";s:6:"Switch";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.4";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 07:10:51";s:12:"post_content";s:198:"<p>This section allows you to create a simple switch for selecting different actions on a page.</p>\n<p>Very useful if you want to create a distraction free purchase page or other call to action.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:55:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-switch/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"d834a3320c292d16e2091604ccda9d5c";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:54:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-switch.zip";}}}i:11;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:19:"pl-plugin-templates";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"pl-plugin-templates";s:10:"post_title";s:9:"Templates";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.5";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-01-14 11:22:40";s:12:"post_content";s:345:"Overview\nSave page templates and custom sections, then reuse them throughout your site.\n\nInstallation & Activation\nTemplates can easily be downloaded from inside WordPress using PageLines Platform 5.\n\nDownload the plugin from the Connect store. It will now appear in your ‘Plugins’ tab.\nClick ‘Plugins’, and find your Templates plugin...";s:12:"product_link";s:57:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-plugin-templates/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"9a83e37baefc5ed9d71bf60f466da7ee";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:56:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-plugin-templates.zip";}}}i:12;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:16:"pl-section-grams";s:9:"post_name";s:16:"pl-section-grams";s:10:"post_title";s:5:"Grams";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.8";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 06:27:23";s:12:"post_content";s:262:"<p>A simple yet powerful Instagram section.</p>\n<p>Add your instagram information and this section will pull in a feed of your instagram posts. </p>\n<p>Control the layout of your posts via several options. Including grid width, feed based on #hashtag, etc.. </p>";s:12:"product_link";s:54:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-grams/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"b741fde7a3729064f25267c139f5765c";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:53:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-grams.zip";}}}i:13;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:22:"pl-framework-pagelines";s:9:"post_name";s:22:"pl-framework-pagelines";s:10:"post_title";s:13:"PageLines.com";s:7:"version";s:7:"10.0.91";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-02-25 12:57:10";s:12:"post_content";s:0:"";s:12:"product_link";s:60:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-framework-pagelines/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"5803a01c0fd2769242c42e13eb3640af";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:59:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-framework-pagelines.zip";}}}i:14;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:19:"pl-section-splashup";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"pl-section-splashup";s:10:"post_title";s:8:"SplashUp";s:7:"version";s:6:"5.0.25";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-08 07:34:53";s:12:"post_content";s:346:"SplashUp is a window height section that provides options to create great looking homepages.\nCombine background color, image or video options with sticky navigation and masthead style call-to-action headers and buttons.\nNote: The SplashUp section also includes another section called SplashUp Nav. This can be used to on pages where you do not...";s:12:"product_link";s:57:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-splashup/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"4d473e0ebe79d1bb3689ffbfcb066a38";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:56:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-splashup.zip";}}}i:15;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:20:"pl-section-resources";s:9:"post_name";s:20:"pl-section-resources";s:10:"post_title";s:9:"Resources";s:7:"version";s:6:"5.0.14";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 06:14:36";s:12:"post_content";s:344:"Resources is an advanced  documentation section that uses custom post types to allow for special search functionality.\r\nTo use Resources, simply add the section on a standard WP page and also on the CPT associated with your documentation pages. \r\nMost configuration options are added via the site settings panel (PageLines &gt; Settings &gt;...";s:12:"product_link";s:58:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-resources/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"a08d401274752cb5741448ffe13e4a82";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:57:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-resources.zip";}}}i:16;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:17:"pl-section-slider";s:9:"post_name";s:17:"pl-section-slider";s:10:"post_title";s:12:"Flick Slider";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.8";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 12:27:22";s:12:"post_content";s:268:"<p>A responsive, flick-able image slider that supports links and text. Make effortless well-displayed galleries with the Slider extension.</p>\n<p>A nice feature of this section is its behavior on mobile browsers. Users can switch slides with the flick of a finger.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:55:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-slider/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"cd3ca2a5e77cab8a856901c61402b757";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:54:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-slider.zip";}}}i:17;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:16:"pl-section-boxes";s:9:"post_name";s:16:"pl-section-boxes";s:10:"post_title";s:5:"Boxes";s:7:"version";s:6:"5.0.12";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 12:19:38";s:12:"post_content";s:304:"<p>Display information easily with Boxes; quickly create columned boxes showcasing icons, images, or numbers for your visitors.</p>\n<p>This section supports 3 modes: numbers, icons and images. Use them for each grid box. You can also easy change the grid and responsive behavior of the boxes as well.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:54:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-boxes/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"7ea35b9f5c7650e5ea4c7c2f42d78a90";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:53:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-boxes.zip";}}}i:18;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:22:"pl-plugin-page-browser";s:9:"post_name";s:22:"pl-plugin-page-browser";s:10:"post_title";s:12:"Page Browser";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.3";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-02-29 12:25:48";s:12:"post_content";s:345:"Overview\nSimplify your process with the Framework Page Browser. Easily go through pages, posts, and everything else on your site from the front-end.\nInstallation & Activation\nPage Browser can easily be downloaded from inside WordPress using PageLines Connect and the Extend engine.\n\n    Download the plugin from the Connect store. It will now...";s:12:"product_link";s:60:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-plugin-page-browser/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"6e4b82af191f67256e08978ca4db9961";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:59:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-plugin-page-browser.zip";}}}i:19;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:21:"pl-plugin-custom-less";s:9:"post_name";s:21:"pl-plugin-custom-less";s:10:"post_title";s:11:"Custom LESS";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.4";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-02-29 20:45:06";s:12:"post_content";s:346:"Overview\nAdd custom LESS code real-time and globally from the front end.\nInstallation & Activation\nCustom LESS/CSS can easily be downloaded from inside WordPress using PageLines Co