.com/extensions/pl-platform/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"64fd2c7bd2499f888b8955960c09179a";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:48:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-platform.zip";}}}i:22;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:25:"pl-section-sitemap-footer";s:9:"post_name";s:25:"pl-section-sitemap-footer";s:10:"post_title";s:14:"Sitemap Footer";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.3";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-02-29 09:12:57";s:12:"post_content";s:345:"Overview\nA robust footer section that allows you to display a sitemap, logo, social links and more.\n\nInstallation & Activation\nSitemap Footer can easily be downloaded from inside WordPress using PageLines Platform 5.\n\nDownload the plugin from the Connect store. It will now appear in your ''Plugins'' tab.\nClick ''Plugins'', and find your Sitemap...";s:12:"product_link";s:63:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-sitemap-footer/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"24da54d022cf6e8fa724fbb444772858";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:62:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-sitemap-footer.zip";}}}i:23;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:17:"pl-section-heroes";s:9:"post_name";s:17:"pl-section-heroes";s:10:"post_title";s:6:"Heroes";s:7:"version";s:6:"5.0.10";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 06:54:51";s:12:"post_content";s:270:"<p>The Heroes section is a super simple way to create awesome feature listings, similar to what you see on many product tours. </p>\n<p>The control of the heroes is 100% real time and you can control their layout, background color and more with the click of a mouse. </p>";s:12:"product_link";s:55:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-heroes/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"cf4f968616082d6623265df3a6d5131d";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:54:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-heroes.zip";}}}i:24;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:18:"pl-section-meg