ect which custom taxonomies or Categories are displayed in the menu.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:57:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-multitax/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"d8eed99b11f2a76b173f1fc4eaa52a49";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:16:"screenshot-1.png";s:4:"file";s:59:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/download/pl-section-multitax.zip";}}}i:38;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:19:"pl-section-loopgrid";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"pl-section-loopgrid";s:10:"post_title";s:26:"PageLines Section LoopGrid";s:7:"version";s:5:"1.0.1";s:9:"changelog";s:51:"<p>=1.0=</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Initial Release</li>\r\n</ul>";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2015-10-15 12:35:46";s:12:"post_content";s:255:"<p>The LoopGrid plugin allow users to easily display their posts in a grid format. LoopGrid can display native and custom WordPress post types with sorting and post count options. Pulling posts with specific meta key and meta values is also supported.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:57:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-loopgrid/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"3df7b5fefdbcf8b2221429270f695e7c";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:26:"PageLines Section LoopGrid";s:4:"file";s:59:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/download/pl-section-loopgrid.zip";}}}i:39;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:19:"pl-section-starbars";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"pl-section-starbars";s:10:"post_title";s:8:"StarBars";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.3";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-03-07 07:16:20";s:12:"post_content";s:273:"<p>Bar graph plugin that animates as the user scrolls down the page. Use them to show data, metrics or other information.</p>\n<p>Allows you to control the order, color and animation of the individual bars in real time. </p>\n<p>Great way to add some spice to your pages.</p>";s:12:"product_link";s:57:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-starbars/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"0f29b48c95cd1783add580096a22e4b5";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:56:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-starbars.zip";}}}i:40;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:21:"pl-section-propricing";s:9:"post_name";s:21:"pl-section-propricing";s:10:"post_title";s:10:"ProPricing";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.3";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-01-31 10:40:01";s:12:"post_content";s:344:"Overview\nAn amazing, professional pricing section. Use to showcase different package options, as well as features included in each one.\n\nInstallation & Activation\nProPricing can easily be downloaded from inside WordPress using PageLines Platform 5.\n\nDownload the plugin from the Connect store. It will now appear in your ''Plugins'' tab.\nClick...";s:12:"product_link";s:59:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-propricing/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"218505a4bfeaedd9a12b85b71b00ec70";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:58:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-propricing.zip";}}}i:41;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:18:"pl-section-popshot";s:9:"post_name";s:18:"pl-section-popshot";s:10:"post_title";s:7:"PopShot";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.3";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-01-31 10:22:35";s:12:"post_content";s:345:"Overview\nAn animated image shelf that creates an animated image pop-up when the user scrolls them on page.\n\nInstallation & Activation\nPopshot can easily be downloaded from inside WordPress using PageLines Platform 5.\n\nDownload the plugin from the Connect store. It will now appear in your ''Plugins'' tab.\nClick ''Plugins'', and find your Popshot...";s:12:"product_link";s:56:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-popshot/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"ac8c1bc206facc03ed1c64cbb4c0266f";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:55:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-popshot.zip";}}}i:42;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:15:"pl-section-maps";s:9:"post_name";s:15:"pl-section-maps";s:10:"post_title";s:4:"Maps";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.4";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-02-12 08:32:18";s:12:"post_content";s:347:"Overview\nAdd a customized Google Map to your website quickly and easily with the Maps plugin. Perfect for contact page maps, routes, or showcasing multiple office locations; support for custom high quality markers is also included, and icons can be easily uploaded right from the plugin.\n\nInstallation & Activation\nMaps can easily be downloaded...";s:12:"product_link";s:53:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-maps/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"87fa28121e7070fb4f31a410930d9b9c";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:52:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-maps.zip";}}}i:43;O:8:"stdClass":9:{s:4:"slug";s:19:"pl-section-videobox";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"pl-section-videobox";s:10:"post_title";s:8:"VideoBox";s:7:"version";s:5:"5.0.3";s:9:"changelog";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2016-01-31 10:46:29";s:12:"post_content";s:343:"Overview\nAn HTML5 video section that allows users to embed video full-width or content width anywhere.\n\nInstallation & Activation\nVideoBox can easily be downloaded from inside WordPress using PageLines Platform 5.\n\nDownload the plugin from the Connect store. It will now appear in your ''Plugins'' tab.\nClick ''Plugins'', and find your VideoBox...";s:12:"product_link";s:57:"https://www.pagelines.com/extensions/pl-section-videobox/";s:13:"download_data";O:8:"stdClass":1:{s:32:"9a9323e938906ab39a51e53336411e58";O:8:"stdClass":2:{s:4:"name";s:0:"";s:4:"file";s:56:"http://deploy.pagelines.io/build/pl-section-videobox.zip";}}}}', 'no'),
